      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Feb 25th Update (Guardrails Strategy Change (3.4))",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "hardBreak"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Discussion: We are pivoting our Guardrails integration strategy for 3.4. Instead of routing through LlamaStack (LLS) as a proxy to the Guardrails service, we will integrate directly with the Guardrails API (FMS Guardrails Orchestrator)."
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "https://redhat-internal.slack.com/archives/C09S4J8TV5Y/p1771859583834929",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "https://redhat-internal.slack.com/archives/C09S4J8TV5Y/p1771859583834929"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " "
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Spike has been created around this to understand the re-work needed from bff side"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
